FOOT & MOUTH DISEASE, CAPTIVE ELEPHANTS - INDIA
*************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail, a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
